The chunk defines the `DirectFrame` class as a base component in Panda3D's DirectGUI system, inheriting from `DirectGuiWidget`. It includes dynamic groups for managing text, geometry, and image elements across multiple states. This is part of the class definition section of the document, which outlines the core structure and functionality of the `DirectFrame` widget.

class DirectFrame(DirectGuiWidget):
    DefDynGroups = ('text', 'geom', 'image')
